#: ../../docs/classes/class_vehiclewheel.rst:19
msgid ""
"This node needs to be used as a child node of :ref:`VehicleBody "
"<class_VehicleBody>` and simulates the behavior of one of its wheels. "
"This node also acts as a collider to detect if the wheel is touching a "
"surface."
msgstr ""

